I find Abandoned Park II, Candyland I, Haunted Hallows, and Teres — under the right circumstances — to be great for kill farming too. Unfortunately, I've never been lucky enough to get a good kill farm going on Justice III, but its potential is clear.

As for my own favorite map, I'm torn between Unix and Wonderland (when it doesn't lag nonstop). Venomous TDM is amazing as well.
